OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening and night with some patchy and
OL,7,Fmainly light rain. Turning
OL,8,Fincreasingly misty, especially over
OL,9,FShetland, with patchy haar. Winds will
OL,10,Fbe mostly light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,13,Frain, some of this could turn heavy
OL,14,Ffor a time. Becoming mainly dry in the
OL,15,Fafternoon with some brightness later.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,18,Fchance of rain for Orkney early on
OL,19,FSaturday, otherwise a dry few days
OL,20,Fwith plenty of sunshine. Winds will be
OL,21,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
